            "text": "A sensitive route (admin/debug/management/internal) appears to lack authentication: '(\"comment\",        \"admin' --\"),'. Sensitive endpoints expose privileged functionality. Without authentication, any reachable client \u2014 including agents operating via SSRF \u2014 can access them. Auth may be enforced globally (middleware), but that is not detectable statically."
